=== Now Playing ===
Contributors: jaredmoody
Tags: comments, spam
Requires at least: 2.7
Tested up to: 2.8.4

Show the music you're currently playing in wordpress.

== Description ==

Now playing retrieves album art from amazon

Currently the only method of updating music is the sendToBlog.scpt file, which only functions on os x.

== Installation ==

This section describes how to install the plugin and get it working.


1. Upload the wp-nowplaying folder to the `/wp-content/plugins/` directory
1. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
1. Enter your amazon API keys on the configuration page
1. sidebar.sample.html has an example of how to add the music to your template(s)
1. Place sendToBlog.scpt in ~/Library/iTunes/scripts
1. Update what is now playing via iTunes by selecting the script from the itunes script menu.


